                <h1>Do Traffic Violations Show Up on Background Checks?</h1>
                <p>Traffic violations can appear on background checks, depending on factors such as the type of check conducted, the state laws, and the duration since the violation. Minor infractions might not show up on certain checks, but serious violations like DUI typically remain visible for years, impacting job opportunities or rental applications.</p>
